* She watched him put out his hand, and walked towards her slowly.
Her beast modes telling her to just slamm into him and knock him to the 
ground, but also to see just how far he tried to trust her before they did.
The mode groaled a little deeper, prowls hand barely an inch away.
She sniffed and took in his scent, finally finding that he had faith that 
she wouldn't attack...or at least hoped so.
With a slightly snarl she bumped her snout against Prowl's fingers, but her 
beast modes got the better of her and she oppened her mouth and was just 
about to slam her teeth into his hand when they just simply stopped when 
they came in contact with his armor.
Simply holding his hand snugly in her mouth.*
